M|How |tx|1. Read your text aloud. If phrases sound unnatural in speech, revise them
M|How |2. A|"wld I say this in a conversation w/ a colleague?"
M|How |tx|3. Check for repetitive sentence structures
M|How |tx|4. Look for clusters of the words listed above
M|How |tx|5. Ensure varied sentence lengths (not all similar length)
M|How |tx|6. Verify each intensifier adds genuine meaning